LOCATION:Singapore and online (Singapore Expo)
DESCRIPTION:AWE Asia is the region's leading annual conference for the Extended Reality (XR) industry, spanning Augmented Reality (AR), Virtual Reality (VR), and related Metaverse technologies. It brings together XR enterprise adopters, solution providers, developers, investors, creators, governments, and media. The conference includes two days of thought-provoking sessions, extensive networking opportunities, and an expo. Ideal for AR, XR, and VR practitioners.
END:VEVENT
