SUMMARY:UX360 Europe: The #1 User Experience (UX) Research Summit in Europe
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260623
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260624
LOCATION:Berlin, Germany
DESCRIPTION:The flagship global gathering for UX professionals and innovators, UX360 Europe brings together leading UX minds to explore cutting-edge strategies, share real-world case studies, and uncover insights that deliver measurable ROI. Covering the entire research journey from planning and conducting studies to turning insights into actionable business outcomes, the event features thought-provoking keynotes, interactive panels, inspiring round-tables, and high-value 1-to-1 networking. It is a must-attend event for UX researchers & designers seeking inspiration, knowledge, and connections, focusing on empowering UX research to influence, scale & lead with the theme: 'From Invisible to Indispensable'.
