BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:49cca0ec183445d91b51494cb716e993
SUMMARY:SmashingConf Amsterdam 2026
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260413
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260416
LOCATION:Pathé Tuschinski, Amsterdam, the Netherlands
DESCRIPTION:A 4-day Smashing Conference on UX and front-end for designers, UI engineers, and UX professionals. The event includes 2 conference days with a single track featuring 12 speakers and 2 workshop days with 6 practical, deep-dive workshops. Topics covered include Design Systems, accessibility, Figma, UX writing, modern CSS, AI, leadership, data visualization, and human-centered interfaces, ranging from research to CSS and interface design. The conference focuses on real-world problems and solutions, offering practical and actionable insights through interactive sessions. It's an inclusive event for 550 attendees, providing networking opportunities, job opportunities, and side activities like morning runs, yoga, boat tours, and photo walks.
END:VEVENT
