BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:d4b63c800efce29a19045c7bf474021f
SUMMARY:The QRCA 2026 Annual Conference is the go-to event for anyone in the qualitative research industry to share ideas, learn from experts, and meet other professionals.
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260202
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260205
LOCATION:San Antonio, TX, USA
DESCRIPTION:The QRCA 2026 Annual Conference is the go‑to event for anyone in the qualitative research industry to share ideas, learn from experts, and meet other professionals in an engaging environment. Whether you want to grow your skills, hear fresh perspectives, or connect with peers at all levels of experience, this conference delivers interactive sessions, small‑group discussions, and plenty of networking opportunities. The in‑person event is built around collaboration and practical learning, with workshops, talks, and events that help you take new tools and insights back to your work. Set in the vibrant city of San Antonio, the conference brings together qualitative researchers from around the world for four days of inspiration, connection, and shared growth.
