LOCATION:Dubai, UAE
DESCRIPTION:DDX Dubai 2026 is a two‑day UX and digital innovation conference for designers, product professionals, researchers, and technology leaders. The event brings together global and regional experts to explore how innovation, design, and digital experience shape the future. Over two days, you can join inspiring talks, panels, workshops, and roundtable sessions that focus on topics like UX, product design, leadership, methodologies, and technology. With around 30 speakers, 12 workshops, and opportunities to network with 600+ peers, DDX Dubai blends practical insights with community interaction. Attendees can connect, learn new techniques, and gain fresh perspectives to take back to their work.
END:VEVENT
