DESCRIPTION:SXSW 2026 is a massive cross-industry gathering of creatives, technologists, founders, and innovators exploring the future of design, tech, culture, and media. While not a UX-specific conference, SXSW includes dozens of sessions and workshops on user experience, AI, design thinking, accessibility, and digital innovation — all highly relevant for teams building better products. Held over seven days in downtown Austin, the event blends keynotes, panels, film premieres, startup showcases, and immersive experiences across multiple venues. It’s an ideal space to connect with forward-thinking teams, discover early trends, and show how easy, fast, and affordable user testing can empower better design decisions.
END:VEVENT
