DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260531
LOCATION:Multiple Locations (Barcelona, Lisbon, Berlin, Amsterdam)
DESCRIPTION:While not specifically a conference, it is the only hands-on design leadership event in Europe, that still fits in most people's L&D budget. Leadership Ateliers is a series of highly focused events designed for designers moving into leadership or deepening their leadership practice. Each edition offers small group workshops and masterclasses that develop the strategic, communication, and people skills needed in modern product organizations. Barcelona supports designers working in complex industries with organizational and technological constraints. Lisbon guides junior and mid senior leaders in aligning design decisions with company strategy. Berlin helps ICs transition into team lead and design lead roles with confidence. Amsterdam supports senior leaders through guided peer sessions that explore leadership identity, AI, and the realities of running design teams.
END:VEVENT
